{
  "stem": "17.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was look at this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, it-- it was tolerated, let's say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we were able to eat proper-- eat-- I mean, we were not starving.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometimes we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We would-- that wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But by no means, we were not starving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was very painful, was very-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was hard to accept.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they were not only strangers that were starving, but they were people in my own family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember I saw once a cousin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her husband was a dentist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He died, and she was left with four little children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw this woman begging on the street, walking from one small store to another, begging for food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was in my own family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The cousins were poor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were trying to help as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But after a while, you get immune to it, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it's hard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's very hard now to justify, but you want to survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Under the circumstances, it's survival.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was-- that-- that was the idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was painful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You saw people dying in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You-- you saw your own relatives being hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And still, you can-- within your means, you can help only so and so much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- maybe ourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because later, when we were working outside of the ghetto, we were smuggling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were bringing food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were exchanging our clothes or stuff of our friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we had this chance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were working on the other side of the ghetto and coming back home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a chance to buy-- to bring food to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I can consider myself a smuggler, and I don't mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I think I am losing, a little bit, this chronological order.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is that OK?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
